(8, '', 'subjects', 'Full Width', '1', '1541154952LVPSXY.jpg', '', '', 'Subjects', '<p>The study of science helps us understand the world around us, but at times, the simplest of questions may have the most complex answers.<br /> That&rsquo;s where we can help. At The Science Academy, we&rsquo;re here to help you make sense of the science.</p>\r\n<p>Our programme focuses on quality learning, guiding students through difficult concepts using simple and easy-to-understand terms.<br /> <strong class=\"txt-dark\">Classes are available every day.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong class=\"txt-dark\">Find out more below, or reserve a spot <a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/PAZtkEgSVYvJ6UEN2\">here</a></strong></p>', 'Subjects', '', '', 'Y', 9, '2018-11-02 16:49:13'),
